      <h2>The Three-Tier Picture</h2>

      <p>
        Not every man over 40 has the same goal. Here's how 120g fits into the broader landscape — and where the optimizer audience starts needing more.
      </p>

      <!-- TIER TABLE -->
      <div class="tier-table-wrap">
        <table class="tier-table">
